  "title": "Project Engineer (C&S)",
  "description": "<p><u>Job Description</u></p>\n<p>· Planning, implementing and monitoring work schedule to meet project completion targets</p>\n<p>· Preparation of progress reports, construction method statements and technical proposal</p>\n<p>· Handling technical and engineering issues</p>\n<p>· Ensure inspection and conduct check on site works</p>\n<p>· Liaison with client’s representative, relevant authorities and consultants</p>\n<p>· Oversee the day-to-day structure works of the project and provide timely updates</p>\n<p><u>Requirements</u></p>\n<p>Degree in Civil or Structural engineering that is recognised by PE Board or Degree Qualification acceptable by BCA</p>",
